Package: bladderCancerProgression
Title: Transcriptomic and Immune Profiling of Bladder Cancer Progression
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jay", "Nagabhairu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A four-stage reproducible pipeline (differential expression,
    pathway enrichment, CIBERSORTx immune deconvolution, and trend
    visualization) applied to a public bladder cancer cohort (GEO GSE13507).
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports:
    here,
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    reshape2,
    ggplot2,
    openxlsx,
    enrichR
